# Assets Exposures Underwriting Facilities Provided Approved Limit Amount

## identifier
de8187

## type
float

## definition
This is the total committed amount, or limit, of underwriting facilities first provided by the reporting party during the relevant period.

Underwriting facilities represent arrangements under which an entity agrees to buy securities from the issuing entity to facilitate their distribution to the market.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.ExposuresUnderwritingFacilitiesProvidedApprovedLimit.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=duration
